Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider  看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕嗎  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者這就是你所說的心潮澎湃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你也開始明白了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道要在這兒擺酒宴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你引以為傲的戰車呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾被Saber給毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難道忘了我的決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該說過要打敗最完美狀態的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的裝備的確有所消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的伊斯坎達爾因為不完美反而超越了完美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上所散發的王者之氣的確是前所未有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你也並非明知毫無勝算卻依然來到我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴比倫尼亞之王  在酒宴的最後我還有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准了  說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如把我的王之軍團武裝上你的王之寶庫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,650)\fs40}Ionian Hetairoi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,650)\fs40}Gate of Babylon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對會創造出最強的軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我再問你一次  是否願意成為我的盟友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們兩人聯手  一定連星辰大海都能征服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你越來越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒有被小丑之外的人說出的蠢話逗笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾  從過去到未來  我的好友都只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這個世界不需要兩個王者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是孤高的王道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我帶著敬意  來挑戰你這毫不動搖的品格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情地展現自己吧  征服王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你算是個值得我親手審判的賊人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個的關係其實很好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候又怎能劍拔弩張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許這就是我今生今世所面對的最後一個對手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會死的  我不允許你死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘記我的令咒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彙集於此吧  我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜  我等將在最強的傳說中銘刻下自己的身影！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人是有萬夫不當之勇的英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠資格當我們的對手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇士們  現在就向最初的英靈展現我們的霸道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管放馬過來吧  霸軍之主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓你知曉真正的王者是何等模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼如此折磨自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為Berserker…必須要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為神父是這麼交代的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神父？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他答應把聖杯讓給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要得到聖杯我就能拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要救我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我們約好的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家還要像以前一樣…一起出去玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我又能見到媽媽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太淺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看得見？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道這把劍的長度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是和我相識的騎士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你的武技  我能看得出你絕對是有名的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此我要求你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你瞭解我——不列顛王亞爾托莉雅·彭德拉貢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然想向我挑戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就請你珍惜騎士的榮耀  道出你的來歷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱藏自己的真身來挑戰我  這和偷襲有什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無瑕湖光？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,650)\fs40}Arondight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞瑟…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭斯洛特騎士…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在圓桌騎士中實力位列第一的你為何會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淪落到去當了Berserker？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭斯洛特？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭斯洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對自己的臣民  你只是一味地去「拯救」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻不知去「引導」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不知去引導…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2\fs48}你只是被那只為他人而存在  名為「王者」的偶像所束縛著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的理想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這個王…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小丫頭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道竟已將你逼迫至如此田地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞…瑟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭斯洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合夢想  意欲成就霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此意志值得我讚賞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  勇士們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們又是否明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的夢  註定是要醒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的前進道路上註定有我在阻擋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征服王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  讓你見識那無盡夢想的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本王將親自教會你這個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  覺醒吧  初開劍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,650)\fs40}Ea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適合你現身的舞臺已經準備好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬頭仰視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天地初開  洪荒世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,650)\fs40}Enuma  Elish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子  抓緊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把劍是能將世間萬物破壞殆盡的對界寶具嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有一事未曾問你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韋伯·威爾維特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可有意成為我的臣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有您…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有您…才是我的王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我願侍奉於你  為你盡忠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望您能為我指引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我與您擁有同一個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彰顯夢想為何  是我這個王者的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而見證王者之夢  並將其傳於後世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,則是你這個臣民的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去  韋伯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要見證一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後活下去將其親口向世人講述
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴他們  你的王有著怎樣的英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我伊斯坎達爾疾馳於大地之上的身影！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  出征吧！布凱法拉斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「榮光盡在彼岸」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因為無法觸及  我才偏要去挑戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌頌霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彰顯霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了那些守望在我身後的臣民！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是不缺這種稀奇玩意兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從夢中醒來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征服王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一次的遠征…也讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心潮澎湃不已…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我允許你繼續挑戰我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征服王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普天之下  莫非王土
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個天下  絕不會令你厭倦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還…真不錯啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這澎湃的心潮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是「世界盡頭之海」的濤聲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:23.45,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,650)\fs40}Ωκεανος
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是Rider的Master嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…他的臣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你真是忠臣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是該有義務為逝去的王者復仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我挑戰你的話  我將會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到的命令是「活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的忠心  值得讚賞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要永遠牢記此時的心志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「他使我的靈魂蘇醒」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「為自己的名引導我走義路」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我雖然行過死蔭的幽谷」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「也不怕遭害」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「因為你與我同在」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你的杖  你的竿」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「都安慰我」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「在我敵人面前  你為我擺設筵席」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你用油膏了我的頭」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「使我的福杯滿溢」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我一生一世必有恩惠慈愛隨著我」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「使我的福杯滿溢」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我一生一世必有恩惠慈愛隨著我」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要奪走我的聖杯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼  Saber！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.91,0:23:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人還真讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是哪門子的玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正希望獲得自己的生命…希望能夠降生！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回家  切嗣！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你一定會來的
